ank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/KNOTFEST?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@KNOTFEST<\/a> &amp; heavy music fans together from around the globe for one-of-a-kind experiences in the <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/hashtag\/Metaverse?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Metaverse<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Discord: <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/7e3UBub6b9\">https:\/\/t.co\/7e3UBub6b9<\/a><br \/>Website: <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/hbD3XtoDip\">https:\/\/t.co\/hbD3XtoDip<\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/uogCxi6qNX\">pic.twitter.com\/uogCxi6qNX<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2014 Slipknot (@slipknot) <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/slipknot\/status\/1516434060268113920?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 19, 2022<\/a><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>Furthermore, as the trio of organizations builds the grand celebration of all things metal, interested parties can expect more and <strong>more digital content<\/strong> to arrive. As a result, fans can look forward to unique NFTs, generative collections, collaborations, and incredible wearables all to arrive on the platform.<\/p>\n<p>What all this means, is a genuine social destination for fans of the genre, allowing people from locations all across the world to congregate, share adventures and discuss the latest incredible sounds. All from the comfort of a mesmerizing new digital universe.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Learn more about the Knotverse &gt;&gt; <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.knotverse.io\/\">Here<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofo